```{r}
dwts_ds %>%
  filter(!is.na(`Carrie Ann Inaba Score`)) %>%
  ggplot(aes(x = Week, y = `Carrie Ann Inaba Score`)) +
  geom_point(position = "jitter") +
  theme_bw()
```
